Home Furniture and Lighting Products
Home Furniture and Lighting Products include sofas, bed frames, mattresses, customized furniture, and intelligent lighting systems eligible for subsidies under the program.

Jinan
Jinan is the city where the 2025 Home Renovation and Furniture Subsidy Program is implemented.

Sanitary Ware Products
Sanitary Ware Products include smart toilets, bathroom cabinets, and bathtubs eligible for subsidies under the program.

Personal Consumers
Personal consumers are the target participants of the 2025 Jinan Home Renovation and Furniture Subsidy Program, limited to homeowners within Jinan city.

Smart Home Products
Smart Home Products include smart locks, intelligent laundry racks, gateways, routers, and smart sockets eligible for subsidies under the program.

Construction Bank Life App
The Construction Bank Life App is a mobile application used by consumers to register, upload property information, claim subsidy vouchers, and process discounts during the program.

data.entity_name: 2025 Jinan Home Renovation and Furniture Subsidy Program
data.content:
2025 Jinan Home Renovation and Furniture Subsidy Program
The 2025 Jinan Home Renovation and Furniture Subsidy Program is a municipal initiative aimed at providing financial support for home improvement and furniture purchases through various subsidies.

Home Renovation Materials
Home Renovation Materials include items like doors, windows, wood flooring, tiles, paint, wallpaper, shower rooms, and partitions eligible for subsidies under the program.

Senior-Friendly Home Modification
Senior-Friendly Home Modification is a category of subsidy designed for making homes more suitable for elderly living that is implemented by the civil affairs departments but detailed rules will be announced later.

Smart Toilet Efficiency Standards
The Smart Toilet Efficiency Standards refer to a regulatory benchmark that specifies water and energy usage levels for smart toilet products eligible for a higher subsidy rate.
